gw.plugin.motorvehiclerecord

Interface IMotorVehicleRecordPlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin, java.rmi.Remote

    public interface IMotorVehicleRecordPlugin
extends com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin
    The motor vehicle plugin will generate the request to the motor vehicle record provider as well as returning the MVR data.
